    - SRH1840
- Meze
    - [https://www.definitive.com/](https://www.definitive.com/)
        - Bellevue
        - Also has B&O headphones

## Things to look for

- Clamping Pressure
- Lighter is more comfy
- Nice ear cups (not hot, but comfy)
- Detachable cable
- Replaceable earcups

# Ear Cup Material

- Memory foam with velour is common and comfy for long sessions





